3 ratemaking" means an alternative ratemaking approach for
4 electricity suppliers that includes one (1) or more performance
5 incentive mechanisms in the context of a multi-year rate plan.
6 Sec. 11. As used in this chapter, "performance incentive
7 mechanism", or "PIM", means a ratemaking mechanism that is
