10 Sec. 15. (a) As used in this chapter, "sustained service
11 interruption" means a service interruption that is at least five (5)
12 minutes in duration.
13 (b) The term does not include the following, regardless of
14 duration:
15 (1) A planned service interruption that is:
16 (A) initiated by an electricity supplier to perform
